Integrating advanced machine learning technology the THINKERS App provides improved features for capturing pages from your notebook. Automatically detects handwritten titles and tags in the subject box of the THINKERS Notebook. Capture any type of notebook page from the same capture window. Advanced handwriting recognition to transcribe written words into searchable text. Improved tag searching On screen editing of note titles and descriptions no need to go into edit screen .

We are working hard to constantly improve the THINKERS App and incorporate new features you want and need. Some of the most recent changes we have made are below. UPDATES: Moved sorting view options for the main screen to the pop up menu to be smoother and more intuitive. Decreased the auto capture time interval for faster capture of your THINKERS Notebook. FIXES: Fixed issue with limited time banner showing after subscribing to THINKERS . Fixed issue with data sync not working correctly when during first setup.

We are working hard to constantly improve the THINKERS App and incorporate new features you want and need. Some of the most recent changes we have made are below. FIXES: Fixed issue with subscription pricing options not working as expected.

The completely revamped THINKERS App is now more than just an app for capturing and sharing notebook pages. We redesigned it to be the perfect tool for capturing ideas of all kinds organizing them in an intuitive and personalized way and sharing and collaborating on them with ease. New premium features include: Three Widgets for quick note capture note comment alerts and most recent note. Capture any type of notebook page image or whiteboard record audio and video scan documents and do it all without needing to use a keyboard. Share individual notes or entire folders with anyone anywhere on any device and your recipients don t need to have an account to view and comment. Automatic transcription and handwriting recognition that gives you helpful searchable text. Opt in to have location data stored with notes includes a map view of all captures Customized folders so you can personalize your organization Secure storage plus the ability to set up optional data sync to your favorite cloud service. And more. We have also fixed minor issues in the latest release of the THINKERS App.
